Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.82,0:00:41.82,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}为错位的焦点所惑 四下寻找说辞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.28,0:00:44.28,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}看吧枯叶起舞 终会化为蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.70,0:00:45.70,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}然后调节到位
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.28,0:00:47.28,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,0)\blur2\be1}然后是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.37,0:00:51.37,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}时过境迁太急 秒速开始不合理
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.87,0:00:53.87,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}全因自己武断的选择开端
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.04,0:00:56.04,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}所以必须做出了断
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.79,0:00:59.80,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}无聊的理由 是停止思考的铁证
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.09,0:01:03.09,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}无法守护应守护之物 那就不要乱出头
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.01,0:01:08.01,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}共鸣 荣光 称赞 都不应奢求
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.89,0:01:11.89,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}不明真相的引力 将常识归于虚无
