Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.73,0:01:18.73,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}不是开玩笑的 幻觉已经开始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.94,0:01:20.94,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,500)\blur2\be1}充满谎言的海市蜃楼
