Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.65,0:01:26.66,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}善善恶恶都无法评议
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.91,0:01:30.91,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}全都变得讨厌 连这都是幸福的结局
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.54,0:01:35.54,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}不行 不要说得如此悲凉 世界依然活着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.83,0:01:37.83,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}即使你会哭泣也还活着
